          "actor": "vawn",
          "text": "You always hum before missions."
        },
        {
          "actor": "maestra",
          "text": "Do I? I hadn't noticed."
        },
        {
          "actor": "vawn",
          "text": "It's the same melody every time."
        },
        {
          "actor": "maestra",
          "text": "Ah, it's an old tune. Helps me focus."
        },
        {
          "actor": "vawn",
          "text": "Superstition?"
        },
        {
          "actor": "maestra",
          "text": "Ritual. There's a difference."
        },
        {
          "actor": "vawn",
          "text": "Fair enough."
        }
      ]
